Leland Orser https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Leland_Orser 0 Leland Jones Orser (born 1960/1961) is an American actor. Orser is primarily a character actor, and has appeared in small roles in a wide variety of films and television series, including Chief of Surgery Dr. Lucien Dubenko on the television series ER.
